column4: China says Qualcomm-NXP antitrust proposals insufficient  still hopes to find solution
column5: SHANGHAI  July 27 China's market regulator said on Friday proposals from Qualcomm Inc and NXP Semiconductors to solve antitrust concerns around their now scrapped $44 billion merger had not been sufficient  but it still hoped to find a solution.
